%spark
import org.apache.spark.mllib.linalg.{DenseVector,Vector}
import org.apache.spark.ml.linalg.{DenseVector => VectorML}
val lossByCountry = packetLossByCountry
    .withColumn("connect_duration", col("metrics_connect_duration").cast("Double"))
    .withColumn("loss_percentage", col("metrics_packet_loss_percentage").cast("Double"))
    
val countryIndexer = new StringIndexer()
  .setInputCol("dimensions_country_code")
  .setOutputCol("country_index")

val countryEncoder = new OneHotEncoder()
  .setInputCol("country_index")
  .setOutputCol("country_encoded")

val pcaVectorAssembler = new VectorAssembler()
  .setInputCols(Array("country_encoded", "connect_duration", "loss_percentage"))
  .setOutputCol("features")

val transformerPipeline = new Pipeline()
    .setStages(
        Array(
            countryIndexer,
            countryEncoder,
            pcaVectorAssembler
        )
    )

val Array(trainingData, testData) = lossByCountry.randomSplit(Array(0.4, 0.6), seed=10L)
val fittedPipeline = transformerPipeline.fit(trainingData)

val transformed = fittedPipeline.transform(trainingData)

val pca = new PCA()
  .setInputCol("features")
  .setOutputCol("pcaFeatures")
  .setK(3)
  .fit(transformed)

val result = pca.transform(transformed)
//result.select("score","dimensions_country_code","connect_duration","loss_percentage","pcaFeatures").show(20,false)

val pcaFeatures = result.select("pcaFeatures")
pcaFeatures.show(10,false)

val pcaFrame = pcaFeatures.map { r => {
  val arr = r.getAs[VectorML](0).toArray
  ( arr(0), arr(1), arr(2) )
  }
}.toDF("country_code", "connect_duration", "loss_percentage")

pcaFrame.createOrReplaceTempView("pca")

%spark
// change the day to see new values. (if calling all data ~34 million rows)
val cleanData = scoresData
    .select(
        "tag_high_packet_loss",
        "tag_high_jitter",
        "tag_high_latency",
        "tag_silent",
        "tag_high_pdd",
        "tag_bad_network",
        "metrics_avg_jitter",
        "metrics_packet_loss_percentage",
        "metrics_pdd",
        "metrics_connect_duration",
        "metrics_avg_latency",
        "metrics_max_latency",
        "score",
        "dimensions_country_code"
    )
    .where(
        col("month").equalTo(1)
        .and(col("day").equalTo(28))
        .and(col("dimensions_direction").isNotNull)
        .and(col("dimensions_call_state").isNotNull)
        .and(col("dimensions_call_state").equalTo("completed"))
        .and(col("dimensions_country_code").isNotNull)
        .and(col("dimensions_country_code").notEqual(""))
        .and(col("dimensions_direction").equalTo("outbound"))
        .and(col("dimensions_edge_type").isNotNull
        .and(col("dimensions_edge_type").equalTo("carrier_edge")
        .and(col("metrics_pdd").notEqual(0)
        .and(col("metrics_connect_duration").notEqual(0))))))
    .withColumn("pdd", col("metrics_pdd").cast("Double"))
    .withColumn("connect_duration", col("metrics_connect_duration").cast("Double"))
    .withColumn("avg_jitter", col("metrics_avg_jitter").cast("Double"))
    .withColumn("loss_percentage", col("metrics_packet_loss_percentage").cast("Double"))
    .withColumn("label", when(col("score")>lit(0.5), 0.0d).otherwise(1.0d))
    .drop("metrics_pdd")
    .drop("metrics_connect_duration")
    .drop("metrics_packet_loss_percentage")
    .drop("metrics_avg_jitter")

cleanData.show(10,false)

cleanData.createOrReplaceTempView("cleanData")

spark.sql("select count(*) as total from cleanData").show
